---
import { XCircle, CheckCircle2 } from "@lucide/astro";
---

<section class="comparison-7">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <h2 class="text-center">Kalo Gak Pakai Sistem... Biasanya Kamu Bakal Gini Terus</h2>
    <p class="text-center intro">Coba liat perbedaannya 👇</p>

    <div class="comp-box">
      <div class="comp-item negative">
        <XCircle class="h-6 w-6 text-red" />
        <div class="item-text">
          <h4>Bingung mulai dari mana</h4>
          <p>Nonton tutorial random, makin pusing</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="comp-item positive">
        <CheckCircle2 class="h-6 w-6 text-green" />
        <div class="item-text">
          <h4>Ada SOP mudah diikuti</h4>
          <p>Gak perlu mikir, tinggal ikutin dari 0.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="comp-item negative">
        <XCircle class="h-6 w-6 text-red" />
        <div class="item-text">
          <h4>Edit lama banget</h4>
          <p>1 video habis 1–3 jam, capek duluan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="comp-item positive">
        <CheckCircle2 class="h-6 w-6 text-green" />
        <div class="item-text">
          <h4>Workflow + AI bantu proses</h4>
          <p>Tinggal copas link youtube, AI yang bikinin video nya.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .comparison-7 {
    padding: 80px 0;
    background: #fdfdfd;
  }

  .container-narrow {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 900;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 16px;
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .comp-box {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .comp-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 24px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .negative { background: #fff5f5; border-color: #ffe3e3; }
  .positive { background: #f0fff4; border-color: #c6f6d5; }

  .text-red { color: #f56565; }
  .text-green { color: #48bb78; }

  .item-text h4 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .item-text p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #555;
  }
</style>
